										</div>
										<div class="col-12 col-md-8">
											<p>At their most simple, processes are actions carried out on a set of inputs to turn them into a set of desired outputs. Most firms carrying out engineering, design or manufacturing have operatives executing hundreds of processes every day. Some of these processes might have evolved gradually over many years to have become tedious, inefficient or prone to error.</p>
											<p>Tom has significant experience developing & simplifying business processes, policies & work instructions. This includes setting up data environments & intelligent template documents to make it easy & intuitive for users to do the right thing without needing copious amounts of training, oversite or error-checking.</p>
