										<div class="col-12 col-md-8">
											<p>It's common for office & small business software to be under-utilised with many features & capabilities not being exploited to their full potential. Especially where the software has an underlying automation platform - like VBA - many of the most tedious, time-consuming or error-prone tasks can usually be automated to some extent, to save time, increase quality & reduce costs.</p>
											<p>Tom has significant experience with the MS Office software suite, as well as with VBA & other supporting technologies which he's leveraged for years to automate tasks for his clients and in his work.</p>
