											<p>Tom has experience planning, implementing, configuring, integrating & supporting software systems that have included: 3D CAD systems (SolidWorks + PDMWorks), BIM systems (AECOsim), CAE systems (Ansys, STAAD), plus several different bespoke business database systems variously involving MS Access, SQL servers, web-based APIs and other proprietary systems.</p>
